data.description: Welcome to your idyllic country retreat, a tastefully updated two-bedroom, one-bath farmhouse on a sprawling 11-acre property. Combining rustic charm with modern amenities, the home provides the perfect blend of comfort, space and style. A new exposed wood beam accentuates the farmhouse charm throughout and luxury vinyl plank flooring, recently installed, adds a touch of sophistication to the living spaces. Updated drywall on walls and ceiling continue to modernize the home. The cozy living spaces are complemented by two generously sized bedrooms featuring new ceiling fans for added comfort. The kitchen boasts ample counter space and the listing includes all appliances, ensuring a seamless culinary experience. The washer and dryer remain with the home for added convenience. A large bonus room with new carpet offers flexibility to tailor the space as an additional den, mudroom, or home office. The property spans 11 gorgeous, non-restricted acres, almost entirely fenced for privacy and security. Extensive grading and seeding have transformed the yard around the home, while pasture areas have been meticulously cleared, creating a picturesque landscape. Embrace the charm of outdoor living with a covered side porch featuring a swing and patio space off the back for grilling. A circular drive surrounds the home and a two-car carport provides shelter for your vehicles. There is a small additional parcel located across the street from the primary property, expanding the potential uses of this stunning property. Nestled in tranquility, this farmhouse retreat offers a unique blend of privacy and convenience.
